	construction. This test driven approach leads to some bug fixes and a lots of
	improvement of the KmerVariantGraph class. The documentation for this class
	has been updated and fixed too.
	
	From now, a KmerVariantGraph can be either built on the fly by adding k-mer to
	variant edges or loaded from a dumped index (see the
	`test_kmer_variant_graph.cpp` unit test file for a quite complete example).
	
	
